#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:7 mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:43
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:370
msgid "Brewing Stand"
msgstr "酿造台"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:8 mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:44
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "库存"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:213
msgid "To use a brewing stand, rightclick it."
msgstr "要使用酿造台，右键点击它就行。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:214
msgid ""
"To brew, you need blaze powder as fuel, a brewing material and at least 1 "
"glass bottle filled with a liquid."
msgstr ""
"要进行酿造，你需要烈焰粉作为燃料、一种酿造材料以及至少1个装满液体的玻璃瓶。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:215
msgid ""
"Place the blaze powder in the left slot, the brewing material in the middle "
"slot and 1-3 bottles in the remaining slots."
msgstr ""
"把烈焰粉放在左边的槽位里，将酿造材料放在中间的槽位里，把1到3个瓶子放在剩下的"
"槽位中。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:216
msgid ""
"When you have found a good combination, the brewing will commence "
"automatically and steam starts to appear, using up the fuel and brewing "
"material. The potions will soon be ready."
msgstr ""
"当你找到了合适的组合后，酿造就会自动开始，并且会开始冒出蒸汽，同时消耗燃料和"
"酿造材料，药水很快就会准备好。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:217
msgid ""
"Different combinations of brewing materials and liquids will give different "
"results. Try to experiment!"
msgstr "酿造材料和液体的不同组合会产生不同的结果，试着去做些试验吧！"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:372
msgid "Brew Potions"
msgstr "酿造药水"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_brewing/init.lua:431
msgid "The stand allows you to brew potions!"
msgstr "酿造台可以制造药水！"
